				that artical sucked. All the guy did was bytch like a school girl. what about all those that got on and played that same day? what about all those that have had no problems because they listened to Sony/VI and upgrade BEFORE the patch? you're naive to think there won't be a few problems but for gods sake, this is stupid already.<BR>
